Data Collection

The app does not collect any personally identifiable information.
All movies, series, ratings, and notes added by the user are stored locally on the device.

Data Usage

Collected data is used only to:
	•	Manage the watchlist
	•	Display personal statistics
	•	Provide a daily AI-powered recommendation

AI Feature

The AI feature provides one daily recommendation based on in-app preferences.
No personal data is stored or shared with third parties during this process.

Data Sharing

The app:
	•	Does not share user data with third parties
	•	Does not use personal data for advertising or analytics

Data Security

All data is stored locally on the user’s device. Reasonable technical measures are taken to protect user data.

Children’s Privacy

The app does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13.

Changes

This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected within the app or on the App Store page.

Contact

